{"tid":2258040,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點心紙老細：拖唔拖糧係睇你返工咩態度。。。。。。。。。","createTime":"2020-10-25T16:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T13:16:07.000Z","uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c3e660cc3536b328d71676cd68401c7062698a34","tid":2258040,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mN2OzJcqmhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmN2OzJcqmhU&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=f7c08e22\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mN2OzJcqmhU</a><br />\n1:25<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad38b195d19d54989ed275437cc52c20c61316bf","tid":2258040,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:58:17.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"afaf483fd9d2c698035312b61b62c18b40d0541c","tid":2258040,"uid":283071,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:22:43.000Z","msg":"我兩間都冇食過<br />\n但點心紙老細好明顯唔抵得人搞得有聲有色過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n講咩都假 拖糧就一定係唔岩<br />\n點講都講唔通 簽左傭員合約<br />\n即使個員工日日番工訓教屌客中出佢老婆<br />\n傭主一方都必須要出足糧<br />\n講話咩最終都解決左<br />\n解決左就代表冇拖過糧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有 佢片中個隻海瑞貢丸Apita都有得賣<br />\n佢唔好去屌柒人地apita<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8d343f8dd4a744132d522e1ffe080c6b6ef24a","tid":2258040,"uid":67823,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:59:23.000Z","msg":"被害妄想症痴線藍屍<br />\n乜鳩都話人抄佢 乜都係人地錯 拖糧都係人地唔啱<br />\n斷章取義到綿香老細都幫埋30<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c6e3d0e387350e95e097a8eefc1f56083ea3c3","tid":2258040,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"咁驚人入同一樣貨 點解唔攬個獨家代理黎做？"},{"pid":"83588055ef3f3b4815d6788418a4db03e0b31d18","tid":2258040,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"根本就唔夠惡又無理據,<br />\n想話人地抄佢又無例子, 講到自己原創, 又咁易被人打敗"}]}